   Two ABC Wednesday night half-hour sitcoms
will switch time periods effective this week, network officials
announced.
   ``Anything But Love,'' which was in a 9 p.m. slot, will be
broadcast at 9:30 p.m. beginning Wednesday. ``Doogie Howser, M.D.''
will move to 9 p.m.
