excellent adult appeal in the 9:30 p.m. time period,'' Iger said.
   ``Anything But Love,'' stars Jamie Lee Curtis and Richard Lewis
as colleagues at a Chicago magazine. It premiered Sept. 27.
   ``Doogie Howser, M.D.,'' stars Neil Patrick Harris as a
brilliant teenage physician still facing the problems of
adolescence. It previewed Sept. 19.
